rju
---

[jackd](http://jackaudio.org/) utilities

- [jack-dl][-dl]: load dsp algorithms from shared libraries
- [jack-lxvst][-lxvst]: jack cli host for linux vst instruments
- [jack-osc][-osc]: jack <-> [open sound control](http://opensoundcontrol.org/) daemon
- [jack-play][-play]: [resampling](http://mega-nerd.com/libsamplerate/) [soundfile](http://mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/) playback
- [jack-plumbing][-plumbing]: [plumbing](https://9fans.github.io/plan9port/man/man7/plumb.html) daemon
- [jack-record][-record]: soundfile recording
- [jack-scope][-scope]: plain [X](http://x.org) oscilloscope
- [jack-transport][-transport]: minimalist [ncurses](http://gnu.org/software/ncurses/) jack transport
- [jack-udp][-udp]: jack over udp client (obsolete, see [netjack](http://netjack.sf.net/))

<!-- [plumb]: http://plan9.bell-labs.com/sys/doc/plumb.html -->

